text.tspan: Draw 1 card + 1 for every type of clearing that has a Tip
Orders waiting: Move all orders down the order track.
Lose 2vp for those which run out of track, and discard them
Draw a card and add it to the first step of the order track
You may add cards from your hand to the order track
Recruit: Any number of times, spend a card per warrior on the
board to place a warrior in a matching clearing
Move Turtles: Move any Warriors 1 space, they may take pizza
Initiate Battles: One free battle and then 1 per matching card
spent. After dice are rolled may also spend matching cards to enable
Throw Pizzas: Move Pizza tokens freely among clearings that have
a Turtle Warrior, or have a tip and no enemy Warriors.
Deliver Pizza: In a matching clearing with no tips, flip a pizza into a
tip. Discard a matching card from the order track, and score vp
based on its position on the order track + 1 vp, per tip in the same
Make Pizza: Spend a card to place a matching Pizza in a Kitchen
Build a Kitchen: Remove a Warrior and build a kitchen in that
